'From Squeak3.1alpha of 28 February 2001 [latest update: #4235] on 6 August 2001 at 12:13:01 pm'!"Change Set:		prefFix-swDate:			6 August 2001Author:			Scott WallaceFixes the bug that could clobber the text selection in an unrelated place when launching a preferences panel in a morphic project."!!PreferencesPanel methodsFor: 'find' stamp: 'sw 8/6/2001 12:09'!containingWindow	"Answer the window in which the receiver is seen"	^ super containingWindow ifNil:		[Smalltalk isMorphic ifFalse: [self currentWorld]]! !